></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong><span style=\"color:#2c3e50\">Отличное настроение</span></strong></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong><span style=\"color:#2c3e50\">Стоимость программы включает страхование транспортного средства и пассажиров, что подразумевает покрытие ущерба, полученного пассажиром находясь в транспортном средстве.&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>', '<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<h4><strong><span style=\"color:#2c3e50\">Transfer airport-hotel-airport</span></strong></h4>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<h4><strong><span style=\"color:#2c3e50\">Hotel for 5 nights</span></strong></h4>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<h4><strong><span style=\"color:#2c3e50\">Transfer hotel - tour agency for the start of excursions (only one side)</span></strong></h4>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<h4><strong><span style=\"color:#2c3e50\">Breakfast</span></strong></h4>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<h4><strong><span style=\"color:#2c3e50\">Comfortable transport service</span></strong></h4>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<h4><strong><span style=\"color:#2c3e50\">Accompanying guide service</span></strong></h4>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<h4><strong><span style=\"color:#2c3e50\">Entrance tickets to historical and cultural centers (except for the cable car in Tzakhkadzor);</span></strong></h4>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<h4><strong><span style=\"color:#2c3e50\">Round-the-clock information support</span></strong></h4>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<h4><strong><span style=\"color:#2c3e50\">Great mood</span></strong></h4>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<h4><strong><span style=\"color:#2c3e50\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\">The cost of the program includes insurance of the vehicle and passengers, which means covering the damage received by the passenger while in the vehicle.</span></span></strong></h4>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>', '<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong><span style=\"color:#2c3e50\">Ավիատոմսեր</span></strong></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong><span style=\"color:#2c3e50\">Մուտքի վիզա</span></strong></p>\r\n	</li>\r